        <p class="text-base text-gray-200">There's only <span class="text-white font-medium">one Z tile</span> in the standard bag — but blank tiles can substitute. Words like BUZZER, PUZZLE, and FIZZLE use two Z's, meaning you need the real Z + a blank. The trade-off is worth it: <span class="text-white font-medium">FIZZLE scores 27 points</span> even with one blank (zero-value Z), because the real Z still delivers its 10 points plus the word's other tiles.</p>
      </div>

